# BEP Generator — Core

**Stack:** React 19 + Vite (frontend), Express + better-sqlite3 (backend), Python + Ollama (ml-service). All start via `npm start`.

**Source of truth:** See **CLAUDE.md** for workflow, layout, conventions, gotchas, quick reference, and token-optimization. Read `.claude/project-index.md` before exploring. Run `npm test` after code changes. Use Unix shell (bash); no PowerShell.
